{"tid":534632,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"死咗SD卡 點由RAW轉返做exFAT","createTime":"2018-01-20T04:36:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-21T07:10:03.000Z","uid":41622,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"37dcbd92f4aae95f5259c10ebb85d925d7bf4ee5","tid":534632,"uid":41622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T04:36:13.000Z","msg":"話說早幾日想同張SD卡做下backup<br />\n點知過完資料就發現手機讀唔到張卡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n試過 cmd 用 chkdsk 見到咁:<br />\n\tThe type of the file system is exFAT.<br />\n\tVolume Serial Number is 1E4C-F3AF<br />\n\tBoth copies of the boot information for this volume are corrupt.<br />\n\tChkdsk cannot continue.<br />\n\tAn error occurred while examining the boot region.<br />\n<br />\n搵到 Eassos PartitionGuru 破解版<br />\n拎到資料但都係整唔返做exFAT<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/123220_a19ddbe22afc139c538bfca41cea40ad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F123220_a19ddbe22afc139c538bfca41cea40ad.png&h=ca5d8ecf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇返 Windows 個 Disk Management 都係寫張卡係 RAW<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/123421_418715ca8a3e333c43494f3b3bbec44a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F123421_418715ca8a3e333c43494f3b3bbec44a.png&h=9193e282&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n張卡係 64GB 但係佢寫只係得 58.53GB<br />\n有無巴絲打識點整呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1059a4f407b66e48a13e4c41d68421c450d0fe0","tid":534632,"uid":48286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T05:19:15.000Z","msg":"64Gb顯示58正常，自己上網查點解"},{"pid":"df329d4c6065a29d8c1ec962dea4d0110bd9f354","tid":534632,"uid":5137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T05:28:16.000Z","msg":"Format左佢再initial做exFAT<br />\n唔好再問點解冇64GB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27270ff363789a36645aec768d1ae96cebcee605","tid":534632,"uid":27597,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T07:10:03.000Z","msg":"電腦行2進制, 個硬碟係用十進制<br />\n所以會少左"}]}